#: ../../docs/user_manual/introduction/browser.rst:213
msgid ""
"open the directory in a terminal window  (:guilabel:`Open in Terminal...`)"
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`In Terminal öffnen ...` öffnet das Verzeichnis in einem "
